34:28.530 --> 34:29.440
What if she came back

34:29.510 --> 34:30.889
and saw keiko living in her house?

34:30.960 --> 34:32.300
She couldn't have.

34:32.760 --> 34:35.489
Keiko would've told me.
I'm certain.

34:38.010 --> 34:40.620
Did yumi have any connection
to the los angeles harbor?

34:41.190 --> 34:44.580
Yeah. We were married there at ports-of-call.

