41:07.380 --> 41:09.100
with the special circumstance of lying in wait,

41:09.220 --> 41:10.940
which carries with it the death penalty,

41:11.040 --> 41:12.710
or I can bring the D.A. In here,

41:12.930 --> 41:14.330
and you can confess.

41:14.930 --> 41:16.440
Maybe even save your life.

41:17.140 --> 41:19.710
Which is a chance
your wife and daughter never had

41:21.190 --> 41:22.630
All I want to know...

41:23.630 --> 41:24.910
really...

41:25.750 --> 41:27.290
is why?

41:28.600 --> 41:30.950
Did you kill yumi and aiko

41:31.050 --> 41:32.670
because you had a new girlfriend,

41:32.890 --> 41:36.020
or was it to save your house
and your business?Is that it?

41:36.090 --> 41:39.210
Did you murder your child
to avoid splitting up your assets?

41:45.640 --> 41:49.030
Do I really seem like such a monster to you?

41:52.240 --> 41:54.180
You look human enough.

41:57.280 --> 41:59.790
Are you gonna tell me
why you killed your wife and daughter?

42:04.990 --> 42:06.650
I have nothing to explain,

42:06.730 --> 42:08.290
and even if I did,

42:08.910 --> 42:10.910
you wouldn't understand.

42:11.610 --> 42:13.300
What about your first wife hosi?

42:13.390 --> 42:14.420
What happened to her?

42:20.340 --> 42:21.790
I never...

42:23.370 --> 42:24.900
laid a hand upon her.

42:24.980 --> 42:28.060
I never touched her except to love her.

42:28.600 --> 42:29.690
I'd never...

42:30.020 --> 42:32.580
hurt...hosi. Never.

42:35.920 --> 42:37.240
All right,then.

42:38.390 --> 42:40.320
I'll just stick with what I can prove.

42:40.870 --> 42:42.940
You smart enough to make a deal with the D.A.?

42:43.020 --> 42:44.700
Or should I arrest you for murder one?

42:51.910 --> 42:54.850
He admitted to poisoning his wife
and child with cyanide.

42:57.030 --> 42:58.460
Putting them in a sleeping bag,

42:58.550 --> 43:00.680
tying them up to make it
look like a ritual suicide,

43:00.800 --> 43:02.070
and dumping them in the ocean.

43:02.180 --> 43:03.370
And this deputy D.A.,

43:03.540 --> 43:04.860
And I told him,I said,

43:05.170 --> 43:07.780
paul andrews is a pathological liar.

43:08.480 --> 43:09.800
So what does he do?

43:10.040 --> 43:11.720
In exchange for a confession?

43:12.350 --> 43:14.120
Two terms of first-degree murder.

43:14.200 --> 43:16.470
But concurrent.Not consecutive.

43:17.230 --> 43:19.210
Paul andrews is gonna get parole one day.

43:19.290 --> 43:21.100
-I know it.
-There's a way around that.

43:22.260 --> 43:24.150
-How?
-Bring him to trial.

43:24.340 --> 43:25.810
I can't do that.

43:25.870 --> 43:27.580
He's already made a deal with the D.A.

43:27.650 --> 43:29.500
