43:29.650 --> 43:31.890
because the japanese helped us
with their dental records.

43:33.300 --> 43:36.310
Japanese helped you with the bodies
you found in the harbor.

43:37.040 --> 43:39.000
What about the first wife?

43:39.230 --> 43:41.260
The one he married at the gloria arboretum?

43:44.000 --> 43:46.150
